<br>
Its not hard, just watch your back in 3rd person view while medding, and always have See Invis up, along with gate. Invis isn't quite as necessary, because if they want to see you, they'll have see invis up, too. <br>
<br>
Its just important to know that once you're OOM you're a sitting duck, so until you know how to handle the adrenaline rush of having someone attacking you while you're at 10mana, run away from a solo fight when you get to 20m, and think you'll be at 0m wihen its over until you're confident to get out of any situation with either a quick yonder or a quick gate.<br>
<br>
So I'll say again:<br>
<br>
Soloing = Easy on PvP as long as you can keep calm when you're attacked.<br>
<br>
Gating = Key to survival if you're not prepared for the attack (IE, not at least 60 mana)<br>
<br>
When Medding - Stay in third person view so you can see all around you. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=seven>Seven</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/17/02 3:28:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=442.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> dodo</span><hr size=1> those are great tips for a pvp server... on RZ im always in 3rd person or invis while medding..... im only 22 but ive only been attacked once and i just ran for the zone that time... <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=442.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showNextMessage?topicID=442.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=442.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.emailToFriend?topicID=442.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.threadControl?topicID=442.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilati